8 An Act relating to discovery; creating the Foreign
Litigation Funding Prevention Act; amending 12 O.S.
9 2021, Section 3226, which relates to general
provisions governing discovery; requiring production
10 of commercial litigation funding agreement upon
request; prohibiting admissibility of certain
11 information as evidence; requiring certain
certification with production of agreement; providing
12 exception; defining terms; providing for
noncodification; providing for codification; and
13 providing an effective date.
